# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Payment — VA & QRIS
#
# Prasyarat:
#   - Merchant sudah dibuat admin (06_admin.http) dan status active
#   - Provider credentials sudah diisi di .config.toml
#   - make migrate-up sudah dijalankan
#
# Idempotency: kirim request yang sama dua kali dengan
# X-Idempotency-Key yang sama → response identik (header X-Idempotency-Replayed: true)
#
# List payment response format: { items: [...], total: N, page: N, limit: N }
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl   = http://localhost:8080
@apiKey    = wpay_test_GANTI_DENGAN_API_KEY_DARI_RESPONSE
@paymentId = GANTI_DENGAN_PAYMENT_ID


### 1. List semua payment (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments?page=1&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 2. Buat VA — Midtrans BCA
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: va-bca-001

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "amount": 150000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Budi Santoso",
  "customer_email": "budi@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081234567890",
  "description": "Pembayaran order #12345",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### 3. Buat VA — Xendit BNI
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: va-bni-001

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_code": "BNI",
  "amount": 200000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Siti Rahayu",
  "customer_email": "siti@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081298765432",
  "description": "Pembayaran langganan bulanan",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### 4. Buat VA — Midtrans Mandiri
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: va-mandiri-001

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "MANDIRI",
  "amount": 75000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Andi Wijaya",
  "customer_email": "andi@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081355556666",
  "description": "Top-up saldo",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### 5. Buat QRIS — Midtrans
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/qris
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: qris-midtrans-001

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "amount": 50000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Dewi Lestari",
  "customer_email": "dewi@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081244449999",
  "description": "Pembelian produk digital",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T12:00:00Z"
}


### 6. Buat QRIS — Xendit
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/qris
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: qris-xendit-001

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Rizki Pratama",
  "customer_email": "rizki@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081377778888",
  "description": "Pembelian tiket event",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T18:00:00Z"
}


### 7. Buat QRIS — iPaymu
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/qris
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: qris-ipaymu-001

{
  "provider": "ipaymu",
  "amount": 85000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Ahmad Fauzi",
  "customer_email": "ahmad@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081311112222",
  "description": "Pembayaran jasa desain",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T18:00:00Z"
}


### 8. Get detail payment (isi paymentId dulu)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 9. Cancel payment (hanya status pending/cancelling)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### IDEMPOTENCY TEST ─────────────────────────────────────────
### Kirim request ini dua kali → response ke-2 identik (header X-Idempotency-Replayed: true)

### Request pertama
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: idempotency-test-key-001

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "BRI",
  "amount": 50000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Test Idempotency",
  "customer_email": "test@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081200000001",
  "description": "Test idempotency key",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### ERROR CASES ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Provider tidak dikenal → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "unknown_provider",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Test",
  "customer_email": "test@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081200000000",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### Amount 0 → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/qris
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "amount": 0,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Test",
  "customer_email": "test@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "081200000000",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}


### Email tidak valid → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "amount": 50000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Test",
  "customer_email": "bukan-email",
  "customer_phone": "081200000000",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}
